subtitle.sub01: What is TOEIC? Why learn to learn and test TOEIC?
subtitle.sub02: TOEIC (short for Test of English for International Communication - International Communication English Test) is a test to assess English use level for English users as a foreign language (not Mother tongue), especially those who want to use English in communication and international work environments. The results of the TOEIC test reflect the level of proficiency when communicating in English in activities such as business, trade, tourism ... This result is valid for 2 years and recognized in many countries including Vietnam.
